---
# =============================================================================
# Knowledge Card 模板（草案 / Milestone 0）
#
# 用途：MindForge Writer 在 Milestone 3 用 jinja2 渲染本模板，把 distill /
#       link_suggestion / review_questions / action_extraction 的输出合并为
#       一张 Knowledge Card，写入 <vault>/20-Knowledge-Cards/<track>/<file>.md
#
# 本模板严格对应 docs/MINDFORGE_PROTOCOL.md §5「Knowledge Card 数据契约」。
#
# Frontmatter 字段是 v0.1 的硬契约：
#   - status 默认 ai_draft，需人工改为 human_approved 才进入长期记忆
#   - source_* / adapter_name 来自 SourceDocument
#   - prompt_version / profile / stage_models 来自本次 run，用于回放与归因
# =============================================================================
id: {{ card.id }}
title: "{{ card.title }}"
status: ai_draft               # ai_draft | human_approved | archived
track: {{ card.track }}
projects: {{ card.projects | default([]) | tojson }}
tags: {{ card.tags | tojson }}
value_score: {{ card.value_score }}
confidence: {{ card.confidence }}

# ── 来源（多源协议） ──
source_id: "{{ source.source_id }}"
source_type: {{ source.source_type }}
adapter_name: {{ source.adapter_name }}
source_path: "{{ source.source_path }}"
source_url: "{{ source.source_url | default('') }}"
source_title: "{{ source.title | default('') }}"

# ── 加工证据链 ──
created_at: {{ run.created_at }}
prompt_version: "distill@{{ run.prompts.distill_version }}"
profile: "{{ run.profile }}"
stage_models:
{% for stage, info in run.stage_models.items() -%}
  {{ stage }}: { alias: "{{ info.alias }}", provider: "{{ info.provider }}", model: "{{ info.model }}" }
{% endfor -%}
run_id: "{{ run.run_id }}"
---

## Source Excerpt

{{ card.source_excerpt }}

## AI Summary

{% for bullet in card.ai_summary_bullets -%}
- {{ bullet }}
{% endfor %}

## AI Inference (low confidence)

{% if card.ai_inference_bullets -%}
{% for bullet in card.ai_inference_bullets -%}
- {{ bullet }}
{% endfor %}
{%- else -%}
_（本卡片暂无低置信推测）_
{%- endif %}

## Human Note

<!-- 留给你写自己的理解。补完后把上面的 status 改为 human_approved。 -->

## Reusable Prompts / Principles

{% if card.reusable_prompts_or_principles -%}
{% for item in card.reusable_prompts_or_principles -%}
- {{ item }}
{% endfor %}
{%- else -%}
_（本卡片未提炼出可复用 prompt / 原则）_
{%- endif %}

## Project Hooks

{% if card.project_hooks -%}
{% for hook in card.project_hooks -%}
- [[{{ hook.project_id }}]]（{{ hook.project_title }}）— {{ hook.hint }}
{% endfor %}
{%- else -%}
_（本卡片未关联任何项目）_
{%- endif %}

## Review Questions

{% if card.review_questions -%}
{% for q in card.review_questions -%}
{{ loop.index }}. **[{{ q.angle }}]** {{ q.question }}
   - 答题要点：{{ q.expected_points | join('；') }}
{% endfor %}
{%- else -%}
_（本卡片暂无复习题）_
{%- endif %}

## Action Items

{% if card.action_items -%}
{% for a in card.action_items -%}
- [{{ a.priority }}] [[{{ a.project_id }}]] — {{ a.action }}（理由：{{ a.reason }}）
{% endfor %}
{%- else -%}
_（本卡片暂无行动项）_
{%- endif %}

## Suggested Links

{% if card.suggested_links -%}
{% for link in card.suggested_links -%}
- [[{{ link.card_id }}]]（{{ link.card_title }}）— {{ link.reason }}
{% endfor %}
{%- else -%}
_（本卡片暂无双链建议）_
{%- endif %}

---
<!--
  说明：
  - 本卡片由 MindForge {{ run.profile }} profile 生成；distill prompt 版本：{{ run.prompts.distill_version }}。
  - 任何字段如果与原文事实不符，请直接修改对应章节，并在 Human Note 中说明。
  - 改完后把 frontmatter 中的 status 从 ai_draft 改为 human_approved，下次 scan 会同步到 state.json。
-->
